{
  "stem": "9725.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the thing would scratch with the bundles would drop on you, you know, with the precision of I don't know how many seconds.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you had to catch them as you are continuously swaying because, you know, the ground was giving away from under your feet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was soft bundles, and it was tremendous silos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know how many stories high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then another day we would go and open the flax in the swamp-- the swamp, and the flax had to be broken open because there were linen threads in that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course the swamp was infested with mosquitoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And since we were all scratched from the flax, you know, the mosquitoes feasted on our blood.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at night-- and I was particularly-- there was one German there who had it in for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One day he tempted me, asked me, you know, if I would like some warm soup or something to eat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "No, he asked me if I had enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I said I was eating in camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I wasn't going to say I don't get enough to eat because it would have been accusing them of not feeding me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And to say I had enough to eat wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was always hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I thought he had other designs, and I was scared, scared stiff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I played dumb.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he singled me out for working at night unloading coal, huge coal trains, you know, and during the day to flax.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the afternoon, first in the swamp or in the silos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is when I one night I figured that's it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm just going to jump.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is what I mentioned in my-- and my father thinking back.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
